# **Standup Wall Break**

**Standup Wall Break** is a glitch that allows the player to destroy breakable walls by performing a **quit-out** at a specific position.

You can not perform this glitch in [Glitchless Categories.](/ds1remaster/glitchless)

## **External Resources**

- **Asylum Wall Break** (Easy: simply stand next to the wall and quit-out). Demonstration: [https://youtu.be/vZbDtSURRdc](https://youtu.be/vZbDtSURRdc) by San on YouTube.
- **Logan Wall Break** (Harder: the player needs to fall onto the cage, continue sprinting mid-air, and instantly jump upon landing to get next to the wall before performing a quit-out). Demonstration: [https://youtu.be/zKVLiv5A6J0](https://youtu.be/zKVLiv5A6J0) by San on YouTube.
- **Gwyndolin Wall Break** (Easy: you need to jump while on the platform just before the wall). Demonstration: [https://youtu.be/xC7P_HIw2Dk](https://youtu.be/xC7P_HIw2Dk) by San on YouTube.

These three are the **most useful** ones.
